						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the temple of Pōlēramma.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1720, Kālayukti, Śrāvaṇa ba. 12, Friday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1798 A.D. September 7, Friday: 54</hi> (The month was Nija-Śrāvaṇa).</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of the temple of Channakēśava by Nārāyaṇa-Reḍḍi, a resident of Chikkepalle, a <hi rend="italic">majara</hi> (hamlet) of Chāgallu.</p>						

						</summary>
